@duranlantinkyo’s AW21 collection is a celebration of being bold and bare from face to body. Key Makeup Artist @mathiasvanhooff contrasted fresh faces with fluorescent false lashes to make the metallic textiles and negative-space silhouettes pop. Get inspired to recreate these runway looks your way with:
🖤Acrylic Paint in Primary Yellow
🖤Chomaline in Genuine Orange
🖤Pigment in Silver, Landscape Green, Rock It Yellow and Green Space
🖤Chromagraphic Liner in Primary Yellow, Landscape Green and Genuine Orange
🖤34 Boss Babe Lash, 7 Free Spirit Lash, 83 Siren Lash, 48 Show-Off Lash, 4 Idol Lash and 80 Romantic Lash
🖤Studio Finish SPF 35 Concealer
🖤Studio Fix Conceal And Correct Palette
🖤Mixing Medium
#MACBackstage
